# AI-Powered Customer Churn Prediction

## Objective

The objective of this notebook is to develop and evaluate machine learning models capable of predicting customer churn for a SaaS company.

Using the feature-engineered Customer360 dataset, multiple classification algorithms are trained and compared to identify the most effective model for churn prediction.

The workflow includes:

- Data preparation
- Machine learning model development
- Model evaluation
- Model comparison
- Explainable AI (SHAP)
- Customer risk scoring
- Retention recommendation generation

The final goal is to help businesses proactively identify at-risk customers and improve customer retention through AI-driven insights.
